most famous and best brands in the world, and there is also a range of restaurants and cafes offering the highest level of service.</p> <p>If you're a sports lover, you'll find a health club equipped with all the sports equipment that includes all activities and games.</p> <p>Bloomfields project is of the highest level of security as it is equipped with state-of-the-art surveillance cameras to convey a sense of security to its residents and visitors.</p> <p>Know More about&nbsp;<strong><a href="https://realestate.eg/en/listings/mostakbal-city?location=9&amp;property_type=apartment">Apartments for sale in Mostakbal City</a></strong></p> <p>it's one of the best projects in the heart of New Cairo, and it's your gateway to a good life.</p> <p>It is one of the most important residential compounds in <strong>Mostakbal&nbsp;City</strong> of New Cairo, and the residential units range from one room to four rooms.</p> <p>It was designed on <strong>415 </strong>acres, 320 acres were allocated for residential units and green spaces, 90 acres for services and facilities, and units range from<strong> villas - apartments - twin houses - townhouses</strong>.</p> <p>Your comprehensive guide of the best <a href="https://realestate.eg/en/blog/el-mostakbal-city-compounds/mostakbal-city-compounds"><strong>Mostakbal City projects</strong></a></p> <h3>Bloomfields Tatweer Misr Location</h3> <p><strong>Bloomfields Egypt</strong>&nbsp;enjoys a unique geographical location within the Future&nbsp;city along the Fifth Settlement and New Cairo between the New Administrative Capital and the Golden Square area and directly in front of Madinaty and this site is one of the most characteristic features of Bloomfields project because it saves a lot of time and effort to the residents of Bloomfields Tatweer Misr compound.</p> <p>Bloomfields project is located 10 minutes from the American University and minutes from&nbsp;Hassan Allam Project and Sabbour Compound and also near the Golden Square area on the Central Ring Road, and Bloomfields project is also about 45 minutes away from the Al Ain Sokhna project.</p> <p>Bloomfields Mostakbal City project is only a few minutes away from Cairo International Air Port, and the same time from the regional road.</p> <p>Bloomfields Mostakbal City project was considered one of the large projects that have been implemented within Al Mostakbal City, located in New Cairo, where many other large projects have been implemented.</p> <p>Browse More Than 1000&nbsp;<strong><a href="https://realestate.eg/en/listings/mostakbal-city?location=9&amp;property_type=villa">Villas for sale in Mostakbal City</a></strong></p> <ul></ul> <h3>Most Important services in&nbsp;Bloomfields New Cairo</h3> <p>The company that owns Bloomfields Mostakbal City project was keen to provide many services to its customers in order to provide comfort and well-being to them, the company did not leave any factor helping customers unless it provided it, the&nbsp;available services include:</p> <ul><li>Providing&nbsp;plenty of quiet areas surrounded by green spaces&nbsp;and scattered gardens, so residents can have a good time away from the outside noise inside&nbsp;Bloomfields Mostakbal City.</li> <li>Spa and Gym with all sports devices needed by the customers at&nbsp;Bloomfields Mostakbal City Compound.</li> <li>Track dedicated to walking and cycling.</li> <li>Having a social club to spend the most fun time.</li> <li>Restaurants and cafes are located in more than one place within Bloomfields Mostakbal City project.</li> <li>Provide gardens for walking and spending a special time in&nbsp;Bloomfields New Cairo Project.</li> <li>24-hour security to protect residents with a number of surveillance cameras to ensure safety at the place.</li> <li>Crystal Lagoons.</li> <li>International schools are available to save time for the residents.</li> <li>There are dedicated areas for parties and barbecue venues.</li> <li>There is a smart home system in the units.</li> <li>A Club House.</li> <li>A commercial area with many malls with all international brands.</li> <li>Many of the artificial fountains that make the place a delight, and the artificial lakes whose waters are characterized by turquoise colors.</li> <li>The availability of a dedicated parking area for the residents of Bloomfields New Cairo project.</li> <li>Many swimming pools with different shape and space are available, as well as many water rides for fun.</li> <li>Having a university within Bloomfields New Cairo project to approximate distances for students.</li></ul> <h3>Space and types of residential units within&nbsp;Bloomfield New Cairo</h3> <p>Tatweer Misr&nbsp;Company took care of the area of Bloomfields New Cairo units within its project and was keen to reduce the population density within its units in order to make the client feel the comfort and privacy, through the construction of buildings containing only 4 floors in addition to the ground floor and each floor contains two apartments, contrary to the prevailing system in Al Mostakbal City, where the permits of buildings are the construction of buildings consisting of 6 floors in addition to the ground floor.</p> <p>Click Here for&nbsp;<strong><a href="https://realestate.eg/en/listings/mostakbal-city?location=9&amp;property_type=twin-house">Twin Houses for sale in Mostakbal City</a></strong></p> <p>The areas and units within Bloomfields New Cairo project varied, including:</p> <ul><li>Single apartments.</li> <li>Duplex Apartments.</li> <li>Townhouse.</li> <li>Twin House.</li> <li>Standalone villas.</li></ul> <p><strong>The areas of these units are different and are as follows:</strong></p> <ul><li>Apartments with space ranging from 74 square meters up to 76 square meters with only one bedroom.</li> <li>Apartments ranging in size from 112 square meters up to 153 square meters with two bedrooms.</li> <li>Apartments ranging in size from 205 square meters up to 285 square meters with three rooms.</li> <li>The area of duplex apartments starts from 207 square meters up to 333 square meters.</li> <li>Townhouse with its area starts from 225 square meters up to 260 square meters.</li> <li>Twin House has an area of 260 square meters.</li> <li>Standalone villas start with an area of 306 square meters.</li> <li>In addition, the company was interested in the idea of establishing villas on the top of buildings and these villas have swimming pools.</li></ul> <p>Browse Now&nbsp;<strong><a href="https://realestate.eg/en/listings/mostakbal-city?location=9&amp;property_type=town-house">Townhouses for sale in Moatakbal City</a></strong></p> <h3>Units prices in&nbsp;Bloomfields Mostakbal City</h3> <p>The price per meter of the residential units start from&nbsp;9750 EGP.</p> <p>Prices for smaller two-bedroom apartments start from 1,072,500 EGP up to 1,267,500 EGP.</p> <p>Prices of larger apartments start from 1,170,000 EGP up to 2,340,000 EGP.</p> <p>As for the prices of standalone&nbsp;villas and twin houses, it starts from 2,681,250&nbsp;EGP up&nbsp;to 3,042,000 EGP.</p> <h3>Payment methods in Bloomfields New Cairo project</h3> <p>The company was interested in providing payment systems that help the entire population and in order for each person to choose the appropriate payment system for him, and the company has announced two systems as follows:</p> <p><strong>The First System:</strong> the customer pays 5% of the unit value as downpayment and pays the rest of the amount over seven years without paying any interest.</p> <p><strong>The Second System: </strong>The client pays 10% of the unit value as downpayment and installments the rest of the amount over ten years without paying interest.</p> <h3>Details about the Executing Company</h3> <p><a href="https://realestate.eg/en/developers/tatweer-misr" target="_blank"><strong>Tatweer Misr</strong></a> is the executing company as it has&nbsp;pumped <strong>28 billion pounds</strong> for the execution of residential units within Bloomfields Tatweer Misr project and has been allocated <strong>5 billion pounds</strong> for educational buildings. Tatweer Misr was founded in 2015, where it was established by a businessmen&nbsp;elite in Egypt: Dr. Ahmed Shalabi, Ashraf Arafa, Hamada Dawood, Sami Zaytoun, Samir Aref, and finally the private consultant of the Ministry of Housing, the company invested 55 billion Egyptian pounds in three residential projects in different places.</p> <p><strong>Major works of Tatweer Misr:</strong></p> <ul><li><a href="https://realestate.eg/en/24826-vacation-in-north-coast-d-bay-resort-compound" target="_blank"><strong>D&nbsp;Bay North Coast</strong></a>.</li> <li><a href="https://realestate.eg/en/183-vacation-in-north-coast-fouka-bay-resort-compound" target="_blank"><strong>Fouka Bay</strong></a> North Coast.</li> <li><a href="https://realestate.eg/en/5053113-residential-in-mostakbal-city-the-lakes-compound" target="_blank"><strong>The Lakes Bloomfields Mostakbal City</strong></a>.</li> <li><a href="https://realestate.eg/en/97-residential-in-al-ain-al-sokhna-il-monte-galala-compound" target="_blank"><strong>IL Monte Galala</strong></a>&nbsp;Ain Sokhna.</li> <li><a href="https://realestate.eg/en/28180-vacation-in-al-ain-al-sokhna-phia-compound" target="_blank"><strong>Phia Monte Galala</strong></a>&nbsp;Ain Sokhna.</li> <li>Marina Il Monte Galala Ain Sokhna.</li> <li><a href="https://realestate.eg/en/5050403-vacation-in-north-coast-salt-compound" target="_blank"><strong>Salt North Coast</strong></a>.</li> <li><a href="https://realestate.eg/en/2543-residential-in-new-cairo-the-vues-compound" target="_blank"><strong>The Vues New Cairo</strong></a>.</li> <li><a href="https://realestate.eg/en/5050314-residential-in-sheikh-zayed-rivers-compound" target="_blank"><strong>Rivers Compound</strong></a>&nbsp;Sheikh Zayed.</li></ul> <h3>Features of Living within a Compound within Mostakbal City</h3> <p>There are many wonderful advantages that the individual enjoys when he is in Al Mostakbal City as it is a great investment opportunity, and also these features are one of the most important things that made the organizers within Mostakbal city&nbsp;pay millions of pounds because of their great confidence in the success of these projects, including:</p> <ul><li>The future city is characterized by its large streets, large green area, and high-end design, in addition to the buildings inside it are with a license that the number of floors does not exceed 6 floors in addition to the ground floor and this is not available in all places inside&nbsp;Bloomfields Tatweer Misr.</li> <li>Life within this city is easy and&nbsp;comfortable due to its facilities and many integrated services in&nbsp;Bloomfields Tatweer Misr.</li> <li>Bloomfields Tatweer Misr is a link between the important new cities, located on the road of Cairo&nbsp;Ismailia on kilo 35.</li> <li>The availability of many services within the city, which consists of shops, restaurants, clubs, schools, malls, universities, and all public services.</li> <li>Security and safety are available within the city and at all project gates in the city, as well as city buses to transport residents inside or outside.</li> <li>The city is located near the New Administrative Capital, New Cairo, and Madinaty, as the city is about a third of an hour away from Heliopolis, and about 5 kilometers away from Al Obour Market, and about 3 kilometers from Al Shorouk City.</li></ul> <p>More details on <strong><a href="https://realestate.eg/en/blog/el-mostakbal-city-compounds/the-cheapest-compounds-in-mostakbal-city">Al Mostakbal City</a></strong> compounds</p> <p><strong>Note that the prices and spaces mentioned herein are for the Second half of 2021, and therefore it is changeable, and we, Real Estate Egypt, are keen to update the spaces and the list of residential and commercial units' types and prices constantly to keep the customer informed of the real estate market changes.</strong></p> <h2><strong>Why choose Mostakbal compounds?</strong></h2> <p>Mostakbal City is one of the most vital and modern areas in New Cairo, as it has a privileged location that allows its residents to easily access many vital and entertainment services.</p> <p>The region is also witnessing a continuous rise in real estate values, which makes investing in the future an ideal option for anyone who wants to invest in real estate in Egypt.</p> <p>Bloomfields Compound comes in the heart of Mostakbal City, as it has many features that make it a unique choice for everyone who wants to invest in real estate in Egypt. Among these advantages are the following:</p> <p>The privileged location: Bloomfields is located in the heart of Mostakbal City, next to the Golden Square and the New Universities District, making it a vital hub within the region. It also gives residents of Bloomfields Mostakbal City easy access to vital services and public facilities.</p> <p>Attractive design: Bloomfields Compound is characterized by a modern and attractive design, as it includes many luxurious facilities and services that make it one of the best residential compounds in Egypt, such as swimming pools, a gym, a running track, sports fields, and gardens.</p> <p>- Good construction: Bloomfields Compound is characterized by good and solid construction, which is very important for investors because it means that there is no need for frequent maintenance and high costs in the future.</p> <p>The right price: Bloomfields Compound offers many housing units at reasonable prices, suitable for all categories of investors, including apartments, duplexes, townhouses, twin houses, and standalone villas. In addition, it is possible to obtain flexible payment plans and pay the rest in installments over 10 years.</p> <p>High return: Experts expect real estate values to rise in the future city in the coming years, which represents a great opportunity for investors to achieve rewarding returns on real estate investment in this area.</p> <p>In addition, Bloomfields Compound occupies a leadership position in the real estate sector in Egypt, as it represents a vivid example of the pioneering high-life concept. Thus, investing in Bloomfields Compound is an excellent choice for anyone who wants to invest in real estate in Egypt, either as an investment or to secure the future of his residential life.</p> <p>In the end, it can be said that Bloomfields Compound is an excellent choice for everyone who wants to live in Mostakbal City or invest in real estate in Egypt, due to its privileged location, attractive design, good construction, suitable price, high return, along with ease of payment and flexible payment plans.</p> <h2>Advantages of investing in Mostakbal City</h2> <p>Mostakbal City is one of the most important new cities in Egypt and has many features that make it an ideal place for investment.</p> <p>Among these features is Bloomfields Compound, which offers many great options for investors.</p> <p>One of the main reasons that make Mostakbal City and Bloomfields Compound an ideal place for investment is the city's prime location.</p> <p>It is located in the eastern part of Cairo, specifically in the new ring road, which makes it a hub for many new activities and growing businesses in the area.</p> <p>Thus, it can be said that the city and Bloomfields Compound are important strategic sites for investment.</p> <p>Another reason that makes Bloomfields Compound an ideal place for investment is the high quality of the housing units available in Bloomfields Mostakbal City.</p> <p>The apartments, twin houses, townhouses, and villas are available in Bloomfields Compound have unique and attractive designs and were designed with the latest technologies and the best raw materials to ensure quality.</p> <p>In addition, investors can use their residential units in Bloomfields Compound in many different ways, including living in them or renting them.</p> <p>This means that investors can get a safe investment and a great opportunity to achieve good financial returns in the long run.</p> <p>Bloomfields Compound has many high-end facilities and services that make it an ideal place to live.</p> <p>Among these facilities include swimming pools, golf courses, tennis courts, health clubs, jogging clubs, and game parks.</p> <p>All these facilities and services reflect making Bloomfields Compound an integrated community with services that suit the personal needs and interests of each person.</p> <p>Simply put, Mostakbal City and Bloomfields Compound are ideal places for investment in Egypt, thanks to their prime location, high quality of available residential units, and high-end facilities available in Bloomfields New Cairo Project.</p> <p>It is certain that investing in Bloomfields Compound will be an excellent addition to any real estate portfolio, due to the attractive return opportunities it provides.</p> <h2>Why choose to live in Bloomfields Mostakbal Compound?</h2> <p>Every real estate company seeks to fulfill the desires of customers by providing wonderful and distinguished housing that meets their needs and matches their requirements.</p> <p>If you are looking for a new home in the heart Mostakbal City, you should consider Bloomfields Mostakbal Compound, which offers many advantages that are difficult to find in any other project.</p> <p>Below we will show you some of the reasons why you should join Bloomfields Future:</p> <p><strong>1. A prime location in Mostakbal City:</strong></p> <p>Bloomfields Mostakbal is located in the Mostakbal City district of New Cairo; It is a distinct and developed area characterized by tranquility and safety. Bloomfields Mostakbal Compound provides you with the opportunity to live in one of the best residential areas in Egypt, where you can enjoy a quiet and beautiful life, a unique lifestyle and picturesque surroundings suitable for families and individuals.</p> <p><strong>2. Real Estate Products for Everyone:</strong></p> <p>Bloomfields provides a variety of real estate products that meet the needs of all family members.</p> <p>You can choose from apartments, duplexes, townhouses, twin houses, and standalone villas at attractive prices compared to the prices of other projects.</p> <p>All real estate units are characterized by modern and unique designs that make living in them more comfortable and elegant.</p> <p><strong>3. Flexible payment methods:</strong></p> <p>You can join Bloomfields quite easily, as Bloomfields New Cairo Compound provides you with a wide range of different payment methods, from a flexible downpayment and installments up to 10 years.</p> <p>This means that you can pay the downpayment that suits you and pay the rest of the value in installments over a long period; This makes living in Bloomfields Mostakbal easier and more flexible.</p> <p><strong>4. Outstanding Infrastructure:</strong></p> <p>Bloomfields Mostakbal Compound is characterized by the complete infrastructure that meets all the different requirements of the residents. Bloomfields New Cairo Compound provides complete services, including swimming pools, a social club, walking and running sports, commercial centers, service centers, and wide green spaces, and this is what makes Bloomfields is a great option for buying real estate.</p> <p><strong>5. Reasonable Prices:</strong></p> <p>In addition to all the previous advantages offered by Bloomfields Mostakbal, the prices offered by the company are reasonable and meet the needs of the real estate market, and this makes them competitive and suitable for Egyptian families.</p> <p>In the end, we can say that your joining Bloomfields is a successful and suitable choice for your real estate search, as Bloomfields New Cairo compound provides you with all the amenities and luxury that call for living in the future and enjoying a new and distinguished lifestyle.</p>


